column5: Only one week till brookie opener!  I already got my gear ready and im waiting on january 1st! Its going to be a good year!
hey Troutboy,  was out with a guy called paul from Tbay yesterday...he was telling me good the brookie fishing is down your way....you lucky so and so...lol.  GO GET 'em
I somewhat started already unofficaly!   Caught one 5lber and 3 smaller 1-2lbers!
